Package: titanicShinySurvivR
Title: Interactive Titanic Survival Prediction App and ML Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alphonse", "Kwizera", email = "kaizera.dev@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application and supporting functions 
    for exploring Titanic passenger data and predicting survival outcomes using 
    machine learning models. Includes tools for data preprocessing, feature 
    engineering, model training, evaluation, and UI integration. Designed as a 
    hands-on project for learning the core components of end-to-end 
    classification workflows in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
